Coefficient of Variation for Count Data
Coefficient of Variation
for Count Data

D = # of deaths ~ Poisson P = # in population where deaths occurred R = rate per 100,000 = (D/P) *100,000
D = # of deaths ~ Poisson
P = # in population where deaths occurred
R = rate per 100,000 = (D/P) *100,000

Var(R) = Var [(D/P) x 100,000]
Var(R) = Var [(D/P) x 100,000]

CV = 100 x [SQRT(Var(R))]/R
CV = 100 x [SQRT(Var(R))]/R
